metadata.name: BESSFREN #1
metadata.description: Bessfrens is a collection of 100 Fren companions made by artist drknss.eth and developer paulmandl.eth. Hodlers of the Fren collection will be rewarded if they hold a Fren and a matching Bessfren. Join our discord to stay updated on our projects: https://discord.gg/CJm7Unrvgr
